"""Spatial outlier rejection: reject tiles whose z10 is far below their
neighbors' z10 median.  Then apply maxlift clamp on survivors.

Autofluorescence-corrupted tiles should be ISOLATED (one bad tile surrounded
by normal tiles).  Real shallow tiles (tissue fold) cluster spatially.
"""
